author: 🌈✨ 𝔻𝕣𝕖𝕒𝕞𝕪 ✨🌈
text: thought about taking a personal leave from work, but the requirements were to talk to my leader and see a therapist for “proof” that it was for real i guess? i changed my mind and decided to go into work today and see how it goes. it was so hard not to cry, but i made it through.

author: 🌈✨ 𝔻𝕣𝕖𝕒𝕞𝕪 ✨🌈
text: i was up all night on sunday. it was 6am (monday) b4 i managed to fall asleep. i’d taken benadryl and it usually knocks me out. 9am came and it felt like a train had hit me. i couldn’t physically move. i called out of work. i was in bed until 9pm. i cried all day. i didn’t eat.

author: 🌈✨ 𝔻𝕣𝕖𝕒𝕞𝕪 ✨🌈
